---
title: Sweet-Soy Lamb Rump with Cauliflower Veggie Toss & Sriracha Mayo
description: Add a little bit of spice to dinner tonight with the help of tangy sriracha sauce to really liven this roast lamb up. On a bed of wholesome cauliflower and veggies and then drizzled with soy mayo, this rump is salivatingly good.
